reviewText: Not one bit of nudity in the whole film.
I got this mainly because it was filmed in a country I wanted to visit, Belize. It is somewhat a sleepy action/spy movie.
The  DVD  was  confusing  at  best.
Bought this because it was filmed i Belize and I've been to many of the places.  Really enjoyed it because of the scenery but the movie itself is definitely a B or worse.
Not a blockbuster folks - but since it was shot in BELIZE and I know one of the principle actors - I am extremely biased.
